type programming language,

1108
01:11:48,680 --> 01:11:50,400
which would be useful for verified

1109
01:11:50,400 --> 01:11:52,240
concurrent
and distributed programming.

1110
01:11:52,240 --> 01:11:55,040
All of this being built on
